<p>I have added the aliases <code>reci</code> and <code>recm</code> for <code>recommit (amend)</code> it. Now I can do it with <code>git recm</code> or <code>git recm -m</code>:</p>

<pre><code>$ vim ~/.gitconfig

[alias]

    ......
    cm = commit
    reci = commit --amend
    recm = commit --amend
    ......
</code></pre>
